  >> CONJ_TAC
  >- (`0 <= 2 pow n * r` by RW_TAC real_ss [REAL_LT_LE_MUL]
     >> `&flr (2 pow n * r) <= 2 pow n * r` by RW_TAC real_ss [NUM_FLOOR_LE]
     >> `&flr (2 pow n * r) / 2 pow n <= 2 pow n * r / 2 pow n`
